{"tid":1044630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[贏] 海洋暖化導致全球魚獲下降5%　中國東海失收比率高","createTime":"2019-03-03T05:01:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T15:08:36.000Z","uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8bc69766b0955ec9893cda4a8838639df80c20bc","tid":1044630,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:01:11.000Z","msg":"海洋暖化導致全球魚獲下降5%　中國東海失收比率高<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190302/bkn-20190302010100847-0302_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190302%2Fbkn-20190302010100847-0302_00972_001.html&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEFT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=ae562398\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190302/bkn-20190302010100847-0302_00972_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n一項全球性分析研究指出，海洋溫度上升已經導致全球魚獲下降了近5%。鱈魚、鯡魚等多種魚類和貝類成為海洋暖化下的受害動物。 <br />\n<br />\n研究指出，在中國東海及北海一帶，魚獲因海水變暖而失收的比率高達34%。這個急速的變化，威脅着全球5600萬名漁民的生計。雖然早有預測指，海洋溫度上升對未來海洋生態系統構成嚴重破壞，但今次的研究結論嚴正地提醒人類，氣候變化已成事實。 <br />\n<br />\n研究人員指出，一些魚類本來受惠於海洋變暖而增加繁殖，但當溫度上升到某個限度時，牠們的繁殖率將會下跌。"},{"pid":"498a1ce9a879666ec0df8554713dcab4996c0bc0","tid":1044630,"uid":46737,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:21:32.000Z","msg":"關撚暖化事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中國人出海鑊鑊都成個海撈上黎，非可持續撈魚怪得邊個"},{"pid":"f0b5c4f6219df703fd1b65ea25f5f08d080eed92","tid":1044630,"uid":11698,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:37:53.000Z","msg":"捕到成個海冇哂魚又懶環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f6bd2a8fa4bd70e3b57f9acfc5b97bf7f668b7","tid":1044630,"uid":4575,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"498a1ce9a879666ec0df8554713dcab4996c0bc0","tid":1044630,"uid":46737,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:21:32.000Z","msg":"關撚暖化事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中國人出海鑊鑊都成個海撈上黎，非可持續撈魚怪得邊個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:40:10.000Z","msg":"冚家剷式捕魚，大魚好食，魚毛又鮮味，中國式食法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df02c9dd9402fbdcc1b4012e995b94b1876ac3ee","tid":1044630,"uid":191762,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:42:01.000Z","msg":"環保對中國漁業失收<br />\n呢度會撐邊一邊呢？"},{"pid":"4c9a79830a0dc12b3a05ee0f04de41bd53597c22","tid":1044630,"uid":52006,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:50:22.000Z","msg":"絕子絕孫式捕魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddbd3d9c3375d9e392550056f24d89e23b3240b2","tid":1044630,"uid":46737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:53:49.000Z","msg":"香港都唔係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲釣友都係冚家剷式釣魚"},{"pid":"de976e359f6877ee90ef37e02944b4fe4710a02f","tid":1044630,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:53:51.000Z","msg":"支那漁船睇怕要流浪地球<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68eaa199ceb53022307af18c5626e7c734e2990c","tid":1044630,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T08:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723bee95cccc8945fe4b51780d9c89ce1635dc67","tid":1044630,"uid":19725,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T08:46:58.000Z","msg":"中國係炸魚，拖網<br />\n<br />\n日日咁拖<br />\n拖幾個月都無撚晒啦<br />\non99"},{"pid":"274c822edc3ad259d6b42f8a69bdbc6ba79fc7ff","tid":1044630,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T08:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />關咩事 比班友知道邊度有鯊魚 同你撈撚起哂上黎都仲得"},{"pid":"af0f2cd35262961941683eec078b546fb4bae9a7","tid":1044630,"uid":46947,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0